casebody.data:
Newman, Appellant, v. Al Castrucci Ford, Inc., Appellee.

[Cite as Newman v. Al Castrucci Ford, Inc. (1992), 63 Ohio St.3d 1202.]

*1203(No. 90-2508 Submitted January 21, 1992 Decided March 4, 1992.) David J. Boyd, for appellant. Taft, Stettinius & Hollister and Timothy C. Sullivan, for appellee.

The appeal is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
